## LineCursor.prev() method

Moves the cursor to the previous next connection or previous connection in the pre order traversal.

**Signature:**

```typescript
prev(): IFocusableNode | null;
```
**Returns:**

[IFocusableNode](./blockly.ifocusablenode_interface.md) \| null

The previous node, or null if the current node is not set or there is no previous value.
